410
00:40:11,366 --> 00:40:13,446
No you don’t!
You don't care about me.

411
00:40:13,547 --> 00:40:14,479
You don’t
care about any of us.

412
00:40:14,737 --> 00:40:16,706
I’ve had eight friends killed
