433
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:13,746
If you were homeless,
starving...

434
00:41:14,030 --> 00:41:16,880
Actually, I take that back.
If your family was homeless and starving...

435
00:41:17,316 --> 00:41:20,069
- What would you do for them?
- I wouldn’t kill someone.

436
00:41:20,194 --> 00:41:24,281
- How can you be sure?
- What difference does it make?

437
00:41:24,407 --> 00:41:25,635
They’re criminals,
desperate ones at that.

438
00:41:25,636 --> 00:41:29,234
They don’t care about
anything other than getting the money.

439
00:41:29,235 --> 00:41:30,632
So pay them, just pay them.

440
00:41:30,906 --> 00:41:34,826
Trust me, if it was an option, I
would do that in a heartbeat.

441
00:41:37,537 --> 00:41:38,496
How many others
have there been?

442
00:41:38,789 --> 00:41:41,292
- Since I got here?
