685
01:15:27,721 --> 01:15:30,933
- It’s over, isn’t it?
- No.

686
01:15:34,186 --> 01:15:36,272
Yeah.

687
01:15:40,902 --> 01:15:43,071
What should I do?

688
01:15:44,989 --> 01:15:47,033
I don’t know.

