779
01:24:57,185 --> 01:24:58,537
- Thank you.
- This will all be over soon, I promise.

780
01:24:58,632 --> 01:25:00,413
I have to go!
Call me right back.

781
01:25:01,268 --> 01:25:03,028
Call me right back. Please!

782
01:25:04,689 --> 01:25:08,355
- Linda? Linda!
- Paul? Paul is that you?

783
01:25:09,419 --> 01:25:11,146
- Tell me it’s you.
- It’s me, sweetie.

784
01:25:11,573 --> 01:25:14,790
Oh my God, Paul! What are they doing to you?
Please tell me you’re okay.

785
01:25:15,909 --> 01:25:18,166
I just saw the news...

786
01:25:18,388 --> 01:25:21,642
That’s okay. It’s all okay.
