790
01:25:30,974 --> 01:25:33,359
I love you so much.
I love you so, so much.

791
01:25:33,383 --> 01:25:37,693
I love you so much. I’m sorry.
I should have listened to you.

792
01:25:38,531 --> 01:25:42,010
Sweetie, I don’t care. I just want
you home. Please come home to me.

793
01:25:42,470 --> 01:25:43,504
I will.

794
01:25:44,236 --> 01:25:46,230
- Swear it.
- I swear. I swear I will.

795
01:25:47,051 --> 01:25:48,116
- I love you. I love you so much.
- I know.

796
01:25:49,773 --> 01:25:51,076
- They’re here!
- Okay.

797
01:25:51,649 --> 01:25:53,528
I have to go.

798
01:25:53,588 --> 01:25:55,322
- Call me right away.
