799
01:25:55,790 --> 01:25:58,358
- I love you.
- I love you.

800
01:25:58,406 --> 01:26:00,092
- Swear it again.
- I swear. I have to go.

801
01:26:00,440 --> 01:26:01,338
Come home to me.

802
01:26:02,393 --> 01:26:03,901
Move! Move! Let’s go.

803
01:26:03,902 --> 01:26:04,902
Paul? Paul?

804
01:26:05,380 --> 01:26:07,494
Corporal, get your men over here!

805
01:26:09,137 --> 01:26:11,149
You have to hurry.
It’s almost full.

806
01:26:11,271 --> 01:26:12,964
Just hang in there!

807
01:26:13,218 --> 01:26:16,612
- I can’t... Are you close?
- We’re almost there.

808
01:26:18,125 --> 01:26:20,223
I can’t hear you! Where are you?

809
01:26:26,635 --> 01:26:27,787
Please open it.
Please open it.

810
01:26:29,970 --> 01:26:31,197
Hurry! Hurry!

811
01:26:31,795 --> 01:26:33,582
Hurry, please!
Hurry!

812
01:26:34,560 --> 01:26:35,324
Hurry!

813
01:26:36,331 --> 01:26:37,544
Oh, God!

814
01:26:38,757 --> 01:26:39,724
Oh my God!

815
01:26:41,001 --> 01:26:42,380
- I’m so sorry, Paul.
